{"word":"ἐνεργέω","slug":"ἐνεργέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐνεργέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐν\">ἐν</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔργον\">ἔργον</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ intr.\">intr.</a> ‘be vigorous in pursuit of an objective’, <b>be active, work, operate <a href='B:470 14:2'>Mt 14:2</a>; <a href='B:480 6:14'>Mk 6:14</a>; <a href='B:520 7:5'>Ro 7:5</a>; <a href='B:540 1:6'>2 Cor 1:6</a>; <a href='B:540 4:12'>4:12</a>; <a href='B:550 2:8'>Gal 2:8</a>; <a href='B:550 5:6'>5:6</a>; <a href='B:560 3:20'>Eph 3:20</a>; <a href='B:570 2:13'>Phil 2:13b</a>; <a href='B:580 1:29'>Col 1:29</a>; <a href='B:590 2:13'>1 Th 2:13</a>; <a href='B:600 2:7'>2 Th 2:7</a>;</b> of effective prayer <b><a href='B:660 5:16'>Js 5:16</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ tr.\">tr.</a> ‘bring about’, <b>work, produce, effect <a href='B:530 12:6'>1 Cor 12:6</a>, <a href='B:530 12:11'>11</a>; <a href='B:550 3:5'>Gal 3:5</a>; <a href='B:560 1:11'>Eph 1:11</a>, <a href='B:560 1:20'>20</a>; <a href='B:560 2:2'>2:2</a>; <a href='B:570 2:13'>Phil 2:13a</a></b> (with <el>τὸ ἐνεργεῖν</el> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ obj.\">obj.</a>). <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐνέργεια\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐνέργημα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}